'''Aggressor Wing''' was a wing of [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|BTL-S3 Y-wing starfighters]] that was commanded by [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Horton Salm/Legends|Horton Salm]] during the period after the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]. Other members included [[Telsij Cayr]] and [[Kin Kian (Sullustan)|Kin Kian]].

==History==
Aggressor Wing was given the task of delaying the evacuation of [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal IV]], in order to prevent the fleeing [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]] from looting the planet prior to the [[Battle of Brentaal IV (Galactic Civil War)|Battle of Brentaal]]. Salm was promoted to [[General/Legends|General]] following this action.

The Aggressors were later instrumental in assisting [[Commando Team One]] in [[Evacuation of Ciutric|liberating]] [[Sate Pestage/Legends|Sate Pestage]] from [[Ciutric IV]], then returning to the theater of battle to save [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] from Imperial attacks.

